{"tid":2228372,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"不容置疑，史上最高質既美食漫畫 TOP 10","createTime":"2020-10-03T13:29:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-04T13:25:58.000Z","uid":75100,"like":3,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"d78a67d8d3f624fc0c0e0ee3000029b172c12f18","tid":2228372,"uid":75100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T13:29:39.000Z","msg":"<ins><span class=\"x-large\">第10名 食戟之靈</span></ins><br />\n上榜原因: 假美食真賣肉，但題材新穎，畫風都靚，同睇得出作者對食物有做過功課，唔似美食的gay佬，勉強比佢第10啦唉<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OiQUqM2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOiQUqM2.jpg&h=947c1e9a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<ins><span class=\"x-large\">第9名 孤獨的美食家 </span></ins><br />\n上榜原因: 講真我覺得麻麻，但比個面真人版勉強第9啦，唔同於傳統既美食漫，佢係會令人想代入其中，拋開工作既煩惱，生活既壓力，睇住男主角食得咁爽係幾正既<br />\n <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/10/03/211751_acfe9bad9d803a3e693e703e1eb113ba.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F10%2F03%2F211751_acfe9bad9d803a3e693e703e1eb113ba.png&h=36afe27e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n <ins><span class=\"x-large\">第8名 格鬥料理人武藏 </span></ins><br />\n上榜原因: 呢本應該相信無咩人知，作者最為人所知既應該係「破壞王」。d美食望落堅流口水，而且劇情好有趣又緊湊，雖然只有3卷，但睇完真心好滿足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N1ueqRv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN1ueqRv.jpg&h=b709f1dc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"81a0ab065ac2b621cae73a24694ffe6954a35d5d","tid":2228372,"uid":263150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T13:30:37.000Z","msg":"插"},{"pid":"7ced0b52c06e8928359d0817b8fe062ff41e8821","tid":2228372,"uid":25345,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T13:31:12.000Z","msg":"味吉陽一"},{"pid":"8039e9b50d34a7e6c5f41ee06072bf61fc820f57","tid":2228372,"uid":16518,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T13:33:07.000Z","msg":"頭三冇日式麵包王既話條list可以收皮"},{"pid":"2ae2708f017d72a8126c1caee18c51582ff19e4d","tid":2228372,"uid":32345,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T13:33:35.000Z","msg":"中華一番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b936a71e9e148009054bb18d0c4bfbd391356509","tid":2228372,"uid":366166,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T13:33:36.000Z","msg":"作完晒未<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54e8144f165e9e4fac228b4fa33e2935a40cacde","tid":2228372,"uid":377617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T13:34:13.000Z","msg":"第十名 一見到就唸起虹色戰隊班op"},{"pid":"46b8f2f4db864e93f7e1d10806abc77b6aa91eea","tid":2228372,"uid":8307,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T13:37:49.000Z","msg":"樓豬又釣魚"},{"pid":"28caae8697506e741be9cfba871e78e87d62ec23","tid":2228372,"uid":75100,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T13:38:10.000Z","msg":"<ins><span class=\"x-large\">第7名 妙手小廚師</span></ins><br />\n上榜原因 : 同樣係細路仔煮飯，我覺得好睇過中華一番勁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無奇怪既異能，有既只係各種新穎既料理方式，望住男主角越過一個個難關，小妹好感動<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9TZeqTP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9TZeqTP.png&h=704cdfd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins><span class=\"x-large\">第6名 舞妓家的料理人</span></ins><br />\n上榜原因 : 呢套係講2個鄉下妹上京，想做藝妓，但其中1個其實想係背後支撐別人，而佢就係女主角。呢套畫風超可愛，劇情又治癒，而且美食仲可以自制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n美食漫畫另一個重點，就係可以自己係屋企重現，呢點值得佢第6<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kZzqxAx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkZzqxAx.png&h=7a00e5fe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9a2352122fb320d16961fce96deda19968fc547c","tid":2228372,"uid":245594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T13:38:58.000Z","msg":"又係名師出PHOTO"},{"pid":"50cdd1df240bd4bcd3cf7e4410abe8cf0ca66301","tid":2228372,"uid":149031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T13:42:22.000Z","msg":"無美味大挑戰？"},{"pid":"e18b90a8e0ee1691740b391e1d9a1ac0edf84225","tid":2228372,"uid":75100,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T13:47:15.000Z","msg":"<ins><span class=\"x-large\">第4名 料理復活王  </span></ins><br />\n上榜原因 : 雖然畫風望落一般，但劇情非常有意思，係講一個大廚去改善唔同餐廳既狗糧，令個頹到仆街既廚師醒覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無錯就好似Gordon Ramsay咁，而且睇既過程會識好多野<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4HofaoH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4HofaoH.png&h=d8f762ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins><span class=\"x-large\">第3名 將太的壽司(全國大賽篇) </span></ins><br />\n上榜原因: 呢本絕對係壽司漫畫既大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔睇本篇都會明，所以直接睇全國大賽篇都OK，呢本咁出名唔講太多，總之望到流口水，好記得中學個陣我睇完，食左一星期爭鮮<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PDX0mwy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPDX0mwy.png&h=63c540ef&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<ins><span class=\"x-large\">第2名 未諗到 </span></ins>"},{"pid":"2a7709d91529c98b5a2c75eb4c9fc98e09e86063","tid":2228372,"uid":284529,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T13:49:21.000Z","msg":"做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />第5名又無....第2名又未諗到"},{"pid":"99dac5c2ce274f9975b3634540874a773f838652","tid":2228372,"uid":91833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T13:50:19.000Z","msg":"刃牙3都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03d098111b4f61ff09b6f12e3e028ea7acb24c5a","tid":2228372,"uid":181318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a7709d91529c98b5a2c75eb4c9fc98e09e86063","tid":2228372,"uid":284529,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T13:49:21.000Z","msg":"做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />第5名又無....第2名又未諗到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T13:57:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73242b8da7a98622cbabe7a2023ccffdf5579565","tid":2228372,"uid":75100,"like":7,"dislike":12,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T13:58:06.000Z","msg":"<ins><span class=\"xx-large\">第1名 日式麵包王!!!!!</span></ins><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">我跟住介紹既係美食漫畫既頂點!佢既力量係可以改變左一個人既一生!! 我細個最撚憎麵包，但睇完之後而家要日日食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span><br />\n<br />\n上榜原因: <br />\n首先佢每款包都好好味，做法都會令你眼前一亮。<br />\n如果話食戟之靈入面既反應係爆衫呢d咁膚淺既野，麵包王既反應就係高質到爆! 根據每款包，都會有唔同既反應。雖然佢有好多難明既梗，但當你接受左就會好似銀魂咁，覺得正到痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然漫畫後期暴走左，但都無愧神作之名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M7tuZju.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM7tuZju.png&h=8f98166e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"809dcd4622d4d34a49b811a81683b62d2deaa260","tid":2228372,"uid":75100,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"03d098111b4f61ff09b6f12e3e028ea7acb24c5a","tid":2228372,"uid":181318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a7709d91529c98b5a2c75eb4c9fc98e09e86063","tid":2228372,"uid":284529,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T13:49:21.000Z","msg":"做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />第5名又無....第2名又未諗到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T13:57:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T13:59:00.000Z","msg":"可能因為第1實在太強，我想表達出佢同第3名就係有咁既距離🚬"},{"pid":"3916489572912870bdf4ed6e4f4f2aa0bae2ec9d","tid":2228372,"uid":75100,"like"